{"id": "32797054336051546572131030716645376", "timestamp": "2026-05-04 23:57:58", "type": "xma_media_share", "item_type": "xma_media_share", "text": "", "raw_xma": {"video_url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DXzUfNpDu8-/?carousel_share_child_media_id=3887540393273631860_66446341391&is_sponsored=false&is_ineligible_for_clips_chaining=false", "title": "macroglide 🗞️ Stop Guessing Market Moves.\nJoin FREE Newsletter (LINK IN BIO).\n\nThe most useful financial models you can realistically build at home are the core ones used on Wall Street: a discounted cash flow model to value companies based on future cash flows, a three-statement model linking income statement, balance sheet, and cash flow for forecasting, a comparable companies model using valuation multiples, a simple leveraged buyout model to understand private equity returns, and a portfolio tracking or backtesting model to analyze investment performance; these models teach valuation, forecasting, capital structure, and risk, and together form the foundation of most real-world finance work.\n\nCredits: Pinterest, 2026\nEdited for educational purposes. No\nownership claimed. This content is for informational purposes only and does not constitute financial or investment advice.", "preview_url": "https://instagram.fods5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/684946428_17937254604213392_6437498007957846069_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1350_tt6&_nc_cat=111&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmciOiJDQVJPVVNFTF9JVEVNLmlnX3NoaW1fcmVhZC4xMDgweDEzNTAuQzMifQ%3D%3D&_nc_ohc=h_yxp2shfA8Q7kNvwGgmDZW&_nc_oc=AdraaGHPLbJ9vpIFzE_JM-UGWiwkwoZFq0ixRyZB0KP_b052w0mIWPjWmZGjCqUscVo&_nc_ad=z-m&_nc_cid=1488&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=instagram.fods5-1.fna&_nc_gid=r6_31WYVpindmsfamFLVVw&_nc_ss=7c3ba&oh=00_Af5nu45kNi0Vhlx0ekNfUQngwpJ6DQ505woow_rJOn7CCw&oe=6A075D81&ig_cache_key=Mzg4NzU0MDM5MzI3MzYzMTg2MA%3D%3D.2-ccb7-5", "preview_url_mime_type": "image/jpeg", "header_icon_url": "https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-19/563552991_17913037251213392_7575904515